Package: artassetmeta
Title: Tag Digital Art Assets with Metadata
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A compact, XMP-first metadata tagging function for original digital
    fine art and derivative media such as still images, GIFs, and short videos.
    It writes identity, authorship, ownership, rights, accessibility, and
    discovery fields by delegating to ExifTool.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
URL: https://docs.artalytics.dev/r/artassetmeta, https://github.com/artalytics/artassetmeta
BugReports: https://github.com/artalytics/artassetmeta/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    exiftoolr,
    fs,
    stringr
Suggests:
    covr,
    knitr,
    quarto,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/Needs/website: pkgdown, artalytics/templ.pkgdown
SystemRequirements: ExifTool
VignetteBuilder: quarto
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
